lead_paragraph: Clayton Kershaw gave up one run and five hits in three innings in his second spring training start, a 7-3 win for the Los Angeles Dodgers over the Chicago Cubs on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Kershaw Gives Up 1 Run as Dodgers Beat Cubs 7-3
